LITA Bath Rug 2 x 4 Non-Slip Quick Dry Gray Marble

18.89 USD

Availability: In stock

LITA bath rug offers a non-slip, quick-dry, and washable solution for any bathroom. With its ultra-thin design and rubber backing, it's perfect for under doors, in front of the tub, and various other spaces. Ideal for daily use and easy cleaning, it adds a sleek and modern look to your bathroom.

This LITA bath rug is the perfect combination of style and functionality. Its ultra-thin construction makes it ideal for fitting under doors and in small spaces, such as in front of a bathtub or beside the shower. Crafted with a super absorbent and quick-drying material, it ensures your bathroom stays dry and clean with minimal effort. The rubber non-slip backing provides a secure grip, preventing any sliding or slipping on wet floors. It's not only practical but also soft to the touch and easy to maintain with both hand and machine washing. With its elegant gray marble color, this floor mat adds a modern and sophisticated look to your bathroom space.","Designed for everyday use, this LITA bath rug is the ultimate solution for any slip-prone bathroom area. It works perfectly in front of the bathtub, shower, sink, and even in the laundry room or entryway. Its lightweight and thin profile allow for easy movement and access, making it ideal for users who frequently open and close doors. With its dual-use capability and sleek design, it's a great gift for any household, including children, adults, elderly, and pets. It's also machine-washable, making cleaning stress-free and maintaining hygiene simple.
